CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1777554668
OL,3,CDrivers warned to be vigilant on roads
OL,4,Cas likelihood of hitting deer rises
OL,6,FBailey Bavister was driving between
OL,7,FAlton and Basingstoke along the A339
OL,8,Fwhen the incident happened.
OL,10,FHe said: "The deer bounded in from the
OL,11,Fopposite side of the road, bounced
OL,12,Finto the road, and then hit my
OL,13,Fheadlight, and proceeded to then roll
OL,14,Fdown the side of the car, so it was a
OL,15,Fbit of grill damage, the underside of
OL,16,Fthe wheel arch, and then as I'm
OL,17,Fdriving that way, the deer's then
OL,18,Frolled down and kind of damaged this
OL,19,Fwhole panel of the door, and then ping
OL,20,Fback off into the other side of the
OL,21,Froad."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
