OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1777554668
OL,3,CDrivers warned to be vigilant on roads
OL,4,Cas likelihood of hitting deer rises
OL,6,FBailey needed a new bonnet, headlight,
OL,7,Fand casing, grill, wheelarch, and door
OL,8,F- causing #7,500 worth of damage.
OL,10,FIn May 2025, a total of 205 deer were
OL,11,Fhit by AA members, compared to a
OL,12,Fmonthly average of 135.
OL,14,FSo far this year, AA members have
OL,15,Freported 454 deer strikes, as well as
OL,16,F1,619 incidents last year.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
