OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1777554668
OL,3,CDrivers warned to be vigilant on roads
OL,4,Cas likelihood of hitting deer rises
OL,6,FThe increase in strikes in May each
OL,7,Fyear as young deer leave breeding
OL,8,Fsites is in addition to the other
OL,9,Fspike in collisions every autumn due
OL,10,Fto rutting.
OL,12,FThe Road Traffic Act 1988 does not
OL,13,Frequire people to report deer strikes
OL,14,Fwith the police, but the AA is
OL,15,Frecommending that drivers do so, as
OL,16,Fwell as the local authority,
OL,17,Fespecially if the deer is causing an
OL,18,Fobstruction in the road.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
