OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1777554668
OL,3,CDrivers warned to be vigilant on roads
OL,4,Cas likelihood of hitting deer rises
OL,6,FTim Rankin, managing director of AA
OL,7,FAccident Assist, said: "Every year we
OL,8,Fare seeing more deer killed on our
OL,9,Froads, with May proving to be a
OL,10,Fpivotal month. While many have an
OL,11,Fidealised vision of Bambi playing
OL,12,Famongst the long grass, the sad
OL,13,Freality is that many young deer end up
OL,14,Fas roadkill.
OL,26,@oD@XOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1777554668
OL,3,CDrivers warned to be vigilant on roads
OL,4,Cas likelihood of hitting deer rises
OL,6,F"Bailey's experience is a classic
OL,7,Fexample of just how shocking and
OL,8,Fdamaging a deer strike can be. It can
OL,9,Fbe very difficult to avoid colliding
OL,10,Fwith a deer, but reducing your speed
OL,11,Fand taking extra care to look ahead on
OL,12,Frural roads can make a difference.
OL,14,F"As the deer population continues to
OL,15,Fboom, we are concerned that 2026 could
OL,16,Fsee record levels of deer strikes."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUxD@cO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
